This is Hadaka Matsuri, this is their 5 Song Demo CD, they hate this recording and I had to beg them to let me release this.  You&amp;#039;re making a mistake if you don&amp;#039;t download this and check it out if you&amp;#039;re into anything like Spirit of Versailles, Saetia, Mohinder, I Robot, Funeral Diner, Orchid or anything like that.  They were often referred to as Screamo, Emo-Violence, Hardcore, etc.  They personally preferred screamo and Emo-Violence though.  They were active from around 2001 to 2005.

Vocals and Guitar - Derek Mullins
Drums - JD Collette
Bass - Doug Allison

